{
  "text": "Oxygen consumption, CO2 production, respiratory exchange ratio, and heat production were measured using the Phenomaster system (TSE) via the Washington University Diabetic Mouse Models Phenotyping Core Facility as described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Metabolic parameters were documented every 13 minutes.",
